{"tid":1353241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【公投】燒唔燒村？？？？？？？？","createTime":"2019-07-23T02:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T16:58:07.000Z","uid":73392,"like":336,"dislike":87,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"6b346f5a3668d88af8c56523e7ee3a4c4ca65688","tid":1353241,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:27:37.000Z","msg":"出面成班係度帶風向，又話圍村外人多過牛屎佬，又引用侯志強話，比錢拆祠堂都得，講咁多咪又係想，咁低件事，政府就最怕亂嘅，一切嘅目的就係唔想再升溫<br />\n<br />\n比你班仆街咁低件事，咁屌人老母，咪唔洗付出代價？同你講呀，呢件事<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就算比錢都要燒鳩你祠堂呀</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">就算象徵式都要，廈村，南邊圍</span>，一定要付出代價<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比打蝦到上心口，要以牙還牙<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要和平非暴力<span style=\"font-size: small;\">牛屎佬：打人唔洗付代價正呀，下次打大力d先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"918fafc7bac763e0eb22a40bcaa20b3f1a0b0bfd","tid":1353241,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:29:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7335a2e709b231f90e938d740ac961242fda9806","tid":1353241,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:30:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8aaf7284a2505b04fb3f3243391c4fd5337c956","tid":1353241,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:31:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a070f66b7563aa6d6a7a5a33fdeae983837c3ac9","tid":1353241,"uid":149342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:31:57.000Z","msg":"俾錢道友做"},{"pid":"5ff857e188f2baddf115c3150123e59bb9692834","tid":1353241,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:32:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d664af0ef54479333122546c2c4e3073cb02b8d","tid":1353241,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:32:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f6941b7ce08f90a5e87b2a30951fe26923ba7d6","tid":1353241,"uid":